IndexMinPQ

public IndexMinPQ(int NMAX)
Initializes an IndexMin priority queue with a given maximum number of elements. All the values of qp[] are set to -1.

Parameters:
NMAX - The maximum number of elements in this PQ
Postconditions:
  • ...
        keys == (Key[]) new Comparable[NMAX + 1]
  • ...
        pq   == new int[NMAX + 1]
  • ...
        qp   == new int[NMAX + 1]
  • ...
        for each i in 0..(NMAX + 1): qp[i] = -1
